I needed some shots, in and around this fort back in 2020 for a short film. It’s a pretty hard to reach location and I had a few failed attempts. Covid then eventually cancelled the film… I am however getting the project back up and running in 2023. So yesterday, I thought i’d get a head start and try nailing down these fort shots. Everything ran perfectly and I ended up with an hours worth of footage which I’m pretty damn happy about… and that’s how I spent Christmas Eve.
Been a while since I was away from the desk. #backstage #gimbalday #canonrf #videographerlife #videogear #runandgun

On the road again. Come and find me… I’ll be exhibiting through October at De Vere Wokefield Estate, Bluewater Kent, Coppid Beach Bracknell and ExCel London at the National Wedding Show.
